data.description: Welcome Home! Come see this beautifully renovated 4 bedroom 2 bath home located in Jonesboro. The kitchen has been updated with stone counters, stainless steel appliances and new cabinetry making cooking and entertaining a delight. The main bedroom and refreshed en-suite bathroom provide a great space to unwind while the additional bedrooms offer plenty of living space to customize as you wish. This cozy home has new floors throughout, updated bathrooms, spacious living room, a deck for family bbq's or just relax in your private backyard.
